The fatal brain-wasting disease is believed to come from eating beef products from cows struck with mad cow disease .The cow was born in Shikaoi , north Japan 's Hokkaido region , in October 2000 , and was checked for mad cow disease after it died , the ministry said .The human form of mad cow disease is called variant Creutzfeldt-Jakob .No cases of mad cow disease have been registered in Bulgaria , where beef meat began to be closely examined for the disease in 2001 .